column4: Home of fast food and an overpriced Barnes and Nobles.
Statue of a fat man. Nobody knows how it got here.
Court made in honor of the Duke of Farlington.
Terrible place filled with radioactive waste and corpses.
Abandonned dorms claimed to be haunted by Salty Beard the pirate.
Pool with a abnormally high acidity. Not dangerous, but the water tastes like vinegar.
